== INSTALL ==
1. Download and install Fluid: http://fluidapp.com/
2. Launch Fluid and Create a new app named 'No Kahuna' with a url of 'http://nokahuna.com'
3. Launch No Kahuna
4. From No Kahuna click on the Scripts Menu (icon that looks like a script near help menu) then 'Browse Userscripts.org'
5. Search for nokahuna or go here: http://userscripts.org/scripts/show/28163
6. Click the 'Install this script' button.